---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Our Mission | Digestive Harmony</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about Digestive Harmony's mission to support individuals and families affected by IBD through education, awareness, support, and research." />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="/">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Digestive Harmony logo" />
      </a>

      <nav class="site-nav">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="active" href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
        <a href="/get-involved">Get Involved</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a class="donate" href="/donate">Donate</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="page-hero">
        <img class="decor hero-leaf" src="/leaf-pattern.png" alt="" />
        <img class="decor hero-butterfly" src="/butterfly-icon.png" alt="" />

        <p class="eyebrow">Our Mission</p>
        <h1>Advancing Hope for IBD</h1>
        <p>
          Digestive Harmony is dedicated to improving the lives of individuals and
          families affected by inflammatory bowel disease through trusted education,
          compassionate support, advocacy, and community.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="story">
        <div>
          <h2>Why We Exist</h2>
          <p>
            Living with Crohn's disease, ulcerative colitis, or another digestive
            condition can feel overwhelming. Patients and families often face physical
            symptoms, emotional stress, uncertainty, and the challenge of finding
            reliable information.
          </p>
          <p>
            Digestive Harmony was created to help people feel informed, supported,
            and less alone. We believe education can reduce fear, support better
            conversations with healthcare providers, and empower families to take
            meaningful steps toward wellness.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card">
          <img src="/butterfly-icon.png" alt="" />
          <h3>You are not alone.</h3>
          <p>We are here to bring awareness, support, research, and hope to the IBD community.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="values">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <div class="small-line"></div>

        <div class="cards">
          <article>
            <h3>Compassion</h3>
            <p>Every patient and family deserves kindness, dignity, and understanding.</p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3>Education</h3>
            <p>Clear, trustworthy information helps people make confident decisions.</p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3>Community</h3>
            <p>No one should have to navigate IBD or digestive illness alone.</p>
          </article>

          <article>
            <h3>Hope</h3>
            <p>Through awareness, support, and research, we believe better days are possible.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="what-we-do">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>

        <div class="two-col">
          <ul>
            <li>Provide easy-to-understand digestive health education</li>
            <li>Support patients, caregivers, and families</li>
            <li>Promote awareness of Crohn's disease and ulcerative colitis</li>
          </ul>

          <ul>
            <li>Share nutrition and lifestyle guidance</li>
            <li>Encourage community connection</li>
            <li>Support research awareness and advocacy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cta">
        <div>
          <p class="cta-label">Join our mission</p>
          <h2>Together, we can bring hope to every family affected by IBD.</h2>
        </div>

        <a href="/get-involved">Get Involved</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div>
        <img class="footer-logo" src="/logo.png" alt="Digestive Harmony logo" />
        <p>A world where everyone affected by IBD can live well and thrive.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>Quick Links</h4>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>Resources</h4>
        <a href="/resources">IBD Basics</a>
        <a href="/resources">Nutrition</a>
        <a href="/resources">Patient Education</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <div class="copyright">
      &copy; 2026 Digestive Harmony. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #08294f;
    --purple: #6e42c1;
    --teal: #0698a8;
    --text: #102542;
    --muted: #52647a;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
    background: white;
  }

  a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3 {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .site-header {
    min-height: 104px;
    padding: 12px 5.5%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.97);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(8, 41, 79, 0.06);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .brand img {
    width: 205px;
    max-height: 86px;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  .site-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .site-nav a {
    color: var(--navy);
    position: relative;
  }

  .site-nav .active {
    color: var(--purple);
  }

  .site-nav .active::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -9px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
  }

  .donate {
    color: white !important;
    padding: 13px 24px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
  }

  .decor {
    position: absolute;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 105px 8% 115px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 78%, rgba(110,66,193,.14), transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 20%, rgba(6,152,168,.12), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #fbf7ff 45%, #ecfbfc);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(58px, 7vw, 92px);
    line-height: .96;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 14px 0 20px;
  }

  .page-hero p:last-child {
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 21px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--purple);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .hero-leaf {
    width: 360px;
    left: -90px;
    bottom: -70px;
    opacity: .08;
  }

  .hero-butterfly {
    width: 88px;
    right: 8%;
    top: 80px;
    opacity: .18;
  }

  .story {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .8fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 80px 8%;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story h2,
  .values h2,
  .what-we-do h2 {
    font-size: 44px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }

  .story p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbf8ff, #effdff);
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 42px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(8,41,79,.08);
  }

  .mission-card img {
    width: 96px;
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 32px;
    margin: 22px 0 10px;
  }

  .values {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 74px 6%;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .small-line {
    width: 76px;
    height: 4px;
    margin: 12px auto 40px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 26px;
  }

  article {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 38px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    border: 1px solid #edf1f7;
  }

  article h3 {
    font-size: 30px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  article p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .what-we-do {
    padding: 80px 8%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbf8ff, #effdff);
  }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 34px;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta {
    margin: 72px 6%;
    padding: 60px;
    border-radius: 34px;
    color: white;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--teal));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 36px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 54px rgba(8,41,79,.16);
  }

  .cta-label {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: 44px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta a {
    background: white;
    color: var(--purple);
    padding: 17px 36px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 900;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  footer {
    background: #f8f5ff;
    padding: 54px 6%;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    width: 185px;
  }

  footer h4 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  footer a {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 10px 0;
  }

  footer p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .copyright {
    padding: 20px 6%;
    color: var(--navy);
    background: white;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .site-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .site-nav {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .story,
    .cards,
    .two-col,
    footer {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 44px 26px;
    }

    .hero-leaf,
    .hero-butterfly {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
